author: @nicamaelast123
text:
Thank you stray kids for sharing your story with us😢 Let me share my story as a STAY

I am literally a JYP STAN, i love all JYP groups. But i am not totally involve to Stray kids becayse during 2018 i was so crazy with other groups😔 not until in 2019 i have read some news and articles saying that one of the member left😢. Many fans were so sad about it, i got curios to the fact that it is a JYP youngest group. So i dig up some informations and watch some videos, HELLEVATOR is the first song i listend to stray kids and i am really obsessed to the song. Hellevator keep on playing in my mind, so i watch other videos and i just dont know when but i just fell in love in Stray kids. I litetally forgot the group i am stanning before because stray kids has steal my heart and even make me regrets why i did not know them before😢. GoLive is my furst ever comeback as a STAY, they exist in my life during my toughest moment because my mom got confined in the hospital during the pandemic. They light up my darkest days and i cant thank you enough stray kids. 

I cannot promise that i will stay forever with you but as long as I am alive, i will always STAY by your side😊. You means soo much to me Stray kids😢 I will protect you and love all of you, Thank you for everything. STRAY KIDS you make STAYs stay😢
